title: Bob Mintzer - 1988 - Spectrum FLAC
description:
Bob Mintzer - 1988 - Spectrum

Included is an all-star lineup of R. Brecker, Peter Erskine, D. Grolnick, B. Malach, L. Gaines, and 14 other players. This is big-band jazz at its finest. The recording was made live to two-track digital, and the music, exceptional from start to finish, deserves it. (AllMusic)
